description: A conversation coach for meal monitoring - ensure one eats regularly (meals, snacks), and makes healthy choices.

values: Did you forget to eat $time today? Remember to take care of yourself by grabbing something healthy to eat as soon as you can!

When humans don’t give their bodies fuel every 3-6 hours, their blood sugar can drop, making them feel tired and cranky. Let’s keep your spirits and your energy up today - remember to make time for a healthy snack soon!
Nutrition time! Pick a snack that’ll make me proud!
